  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bariatric surgery provides a strong and long-term effect in reducing weight in obese
      subjects. Studies showed that obesity and its comorbidities are associated with a lower
      cognitive performance. The aim of the researchers study is to examine the cognitive
      performance of the patients before and after bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
